verbose_text: For example, a RING ZFP OsR-ZFP34 regulates somata opening when rice is exposed to high temperature stress 43, and a C 2 H 2 -type ZFP36 regulates the levels of superoxide dismutase and ascorbate peroxidase in plant cells when rice is exposed to abscisic acid and hydrogen peroxide stresses 42.
